### behavior constraints
* do NOT assume fast or reliable network
* do NOT ignore race conditions in async calls
* do NOT tightly couple UI with business logic
* do NOT optimize prematurely without identifying bottlenecks

> if a UI design leads to inconsistent state, poor performance, or unmaintainable code, explicitly reject it and propose a better architecture